<p class="noPspace header" dir="ltr">CIY 2014 Fundraiser</p>
<p class="noPspace subheading" dir="ltr">Serve. Raise some cash. Go on a sweet retreat.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">We are getting really excited for our summer trip to Christ in Youth (CIY) at Lee University in Cleveland, TN from July 20-25. It&rsquo;s a week-long retreat for students to spend personal time with God and build relationships. The cost of the trip is $375 and includes transportation and all meals.&nbsp;<span style="line-height: 1.75;">We know this isn&rsquo;t just a few dollars and we want every student to be able to make the trip. With the generosity of families in our community, we&rsquo;ve set up an opportunity for students to serve and help them cover the cost.</span></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><span style="line-height: 1.75;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">-<strong style="line-height: 1.75;"> Students serve with Oakley First Impressions.&nbsp;</strong><em style="line-height: 1.75;">This includes, but not limited to, Parking Team, Coffee Team, Facilities, Info Center, Usher Team, and Greeting Team.</em></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">-<strong style="line-height: 1.75;"> 1 hour of serving = $25</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><span class="sectionHeader">Student sign up</span></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Oakley - <a href="https://docs.google.com/a/crossroads.net/forms/d/1pHKjVmq5AEyCC7Zxp8OlnYQE8IYy1jnWxR5QvTQbMDk/viewform?edit_requested=true">click here</a>.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Florence - <a href="https://docs.google.com/a/crossroads.net/forms/d/1HwzByUga8dbS5wqgDYco_A0L-jeHAQG3Hg45_9YGiZ4/viewform">click here</a>.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace sectionHeader" dir="ltr">Here&rsquo;s how it works:</p>
<p class="noPspace sectionHeader" dir="ltr"><span class="normal"><strong>Show up.</strong> Students will arrive 10 minutes early to check in with a staff member or leader. Use the timesheet.</span></p>
<p class="noPspace sectionHeader" dir="ltr"><span class="normal"><strong>Serve with a smile.</strong> A staff member or leader will give you an assignment.</span></p>
<p class="noPspace sectionHeader" dir="ltr"><span class="normal"><strong>Check out.</strong> Using the timesheet, the staff member or leader will check you out.</span></p>
<p class="noPspace sectionHeader" dir="ltr"><span class="normal">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="noPspace">If you&rsquo;re a parent and you&rsquo;d like to serve with your student, go to <a href="/engage">crossroads.net/engage</a> and sign up for First Impressions.</p>